# Deployment build/cache artifacts (regenerable; never commit).
# The AgentCore toolkit writes these into whatever directory it launches from,
# so ignore both the intended deployment/ location and the repo root (a launch
# run from the root leaves 20MB+ dependencies.zip / Dockerfile / config here).
deployment/dependencies.zip
deployment/dependencies.hash
